        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "and by those that govern affairs"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "on the Day when the quaker quakes"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "and the successor follows upon it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "Hearts that Day shall tremble"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "with eyes humbled"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "They will say, “Are we to be restored as we were before"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "What! When we have become decayed bones?”"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "They say, “This, then, would be a ruinous return!”"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "Yet it shall be but a single cry"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "then, behold, they will be upon a wide expanse"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "Hast thou heard tell of Moses"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "when his Lord called out to him in the holy valley of ?uwa"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "“Go unto Pharaoh! Truly he has rebelled"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "And say, ‘Dost thou wish to be purified"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "and that I guide thee to thy Lord that thou mightest have fear?’”"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "Then he showed him the greatest sign"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "But he denied and disobeyed"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "Then turned his back, moving swiftly"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "Then he gathered and proclaimed"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "and said, “I am your lord most high.”"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 79,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "So God seized him with a punishment exemplary in the Hereafter and in this world"
        },
        {
